name: ASTEROID I. GENESIS. RED VELVET. ROCKSOLID COLLECTION
description: Our Genesis work. First asteroid from our ROCKSOLID conceptual art collection. This collection of metamorphic rocks based on experimental stage of our years long multidisciplinary research, project INTERFACE. Collection is represented by a number of solid bodies of earth material with the rich texture, geometry and structure. Every meteorite from our collection is unique. And will only come as 1 of 1.
